Work-History/*/
!Work-History/*/summaries/
!Work-History/*/summaries/**
!Work-History/inbox/
Work-History/inbox/*
!Work-History/inbox/README.md

# PDF text extractions (generated locally from source PDFs)
**/*.pdftext.txt

